[Switching from slaughter to vaccination is a major policy change and
signals a shift from rapid eradication to a slower process as demonstrating
freedom from FMD after vaccination is a long drawn out affair. The
scientific basis of the Spanish decision to deny landing to these rhinos &
giraffes is unclear as they would have had any necessary blood samples and
blood test results before the shipment left Natal, much less approached
Spain. At this time there are no reports of any wildlife cases in KwaZulu
Natal. - Mod.MHJ
